resources.string: Amasevisi okufinyelela anikwe amandla kodwa awasebenzi, ungazama ukunika amandla kabusha noma ukuqalisa kabusha ifoni yakho
Yehlulekile ukunika amandla isevisi yokufinyeleleka ngamalungelo ezimpande
Sebenzisa isevisi yangaphambili ukuze ugcine uhlelo lwakho lokusebenza lusebenza
Imisebenzi yesevisi yokufinyelela kufanele inikwe amandla ukuze isetshenziswe (igodliwe)
Kufanele uvule iwindi elintantayo ukuze ubuke ilogu (into egodliwe)
Ngemva kokuvula, ukusebenzisa iskripthi kuzovula ngokuzenzakalelayo isevisi yokufinyeleleka ngamalungelo e-Root (into egodliwe)
Nika amandla ngokuzenzakalela amasevisi ngamalungelo ezimpande
Ukuhlaziywa kwesakhiwo kuzinze kakhulu uma kunikwe amandla, kodwa inombolo encane yeskripthi ingase ingasebenzi kahle. Qala kabusha isevisi yokufinyeleleka ukuze isebenze
Qalisa iskripthi ngokuqondile ngemva kokuvula uhlelo lokusebenza
I-interface yelogi ayiboniswa, futhi ukusekelwa kweskripthi kuyadingeka ukuze uvule lesi sikhombimsebenzisi ngokuzayo
Iphasiwedi kumele ibe nkulu kunezinhlamvu ezi-5

Isofthiwe idinga ukuvula \"Izinsizakalo Zokufinyeleleka\" ukuze isebenze, sicela uvule \"Izilungiselelo->Izinsizakalo Zokufinyeleleka\" noma \"Izilungiselelo->Izinsizakalo Zokufinyeleleka->Izinsizakalo Ezilandiwe Ezengeziwe\", thola \" %s \", bese uvula Amasevisi Okufinyelela
Ibha yesaziso izohlala ibonisa isaziso sokuthi \"Lolu hlelo lokusebenza luyasebenza\" ukuze kugcinwe uhlelo lusebenza
Idinga imvume ukuze uvule isixhumi esibonakalayo ngemuva
Idinga imvume yokuvula isixhumi esibonakalayo ngemuva ukuze isebenze, sicela uye kuzilungiselelo ukuze uvule
Sicela unike amandla izimvume ngaphambi kokuqalisa!
